Akshay Tambe in Nasik (Nashik), India.
This is a 2 week old puppy. She has heard from all of you btw, all of you who celebrated Diwali.
She seemed a little off this morning, so I drove her to the vet. And here she is; dead. Ready to be buried.
I held a dead puppy in my hands today.
Hope you'll have a great Diwali.
Happy Diwali.
